ects-of-orientation-blinds-and-overhangs-on-energy-efficiency-and-carbon-emissions.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Dec 2025 10:16:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2025/12/optimization-of-the-performance-of-double-skin-facades-across-six-climates-effects-of-orientation-blinds-and-overhangs-on-energy-efficiency-and-carbon-emissions</guid></item></channel></rss>